{"word":"G2227 - ζωοποιέω - zōopoiéō - dzo-op-oy-eh'-o - Make alive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ζωοποιέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">zōopoiéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dzo-op-oy-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make alive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உயிர்ப்பி, உயிர்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to produce alive, beget or bear living young"},{"paragraph":"2. to cause to live, make alive, give life"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2226 - ζῶον - zōon - dzo'-on/2226\">G2226</a> and <a href=\"#/G4160 - ποιέω - poiéō - poy-eh'-o/4160\">G4160</a>; to (<i>re-</i>) <i>vitalize</i> (literally or figuratively): - make alive, give life, quicken.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1186/1186\">G1186</a>, <a href=\"#/G2198/2198\">G2198</a>, <a href=\"#/G2222/2222\">G2222</a>, <a href=\"#/G2225/2225\">G2225</a>, <a href=\"#/G2226/2226\">G2226</a>, <a href=\"#/G2227/2227\">G2227</a>, <a href=\"#/G326/326\">G326</a>"}]}